   featured research prototype resulting from our reflections on the
   software design process. CoffeeTable exchanges the traditional IDE for
   one built around a shared interactive desk. The proposed solution
   encourages smooth transitions between agile and traditional modes of
   working whilst helping to create a shared vision and common reference
