   the data. The data were collected using two questionnaires. The
   population of the first study contains more than 100 respondents from
   three different continents (Europe, North America, and Asia) and seven
   different countries and the second study 500 respondents from the same
   organization. The results reveal that most respondents are satisfied
   agile way of working and would like to stay in agile mode. They also
