Abstract = {Choosing the appropriate software development methodology is something
   which continues to occupy the minds of many IT professionals. The
   introduction of ``Agile{''} development methodologies such as XP and
   SCRUM held the promise of improved software quality and reduced delivery
   times. Combined with a Lean philosophy, there would seem to be potential
