   team deals with requirement collection, analysis, design, coding and
   unit testing; the QA/QC team performs software tests and regression in a
   production-like environment. The systems/operations team focuses on the
   hardware and system software preparation and support, receives and
   installs new code releases after QA approval and monitors systems
   operations. We are vying to perform new code releases twice a month. The
   method has worked well during the four years of the system development
   phase and has allowed for a constant support of VENUS. DMAS will be
