Abstract = {RUP is a comprehensive software development process framework that has
   gained a lot of interest by the industry. One major challenge of taking
   RUP into use is to tailor it to specific needs and then to introduce it
   into a development organization. This study presents a review and a
   systematic assembly of existing studies on the tailoring and
   introduction of RUP. From a systematic search for study reports on this
   topic we found that most research is anecdotal and focus on the effects
   of RUP itself. Only a few number of studies address tailoring and
   introduction. We have found that tailoring RUP is a considerable
