Abstract = {The DICE1 framework provides means for predicting the outcome of change
   management initiatives. The four factors: duration, integrity,
   commitment, and effort are evaluated and a score is calculated. The DICE
   (R) score is used to classify projects into win, worry, or woe zones. In
   this paper, we apply the DICE (R) framework to predict the outcome of a
