   this paper, Extreme Programming (XP) was evaluated in a distributed
   legacy system reengineering project to handle the imperfect system
   requirement and response to rapid business request combination while the
   customer was offshore. Some important adjustment was made to the XP
   process according to the project environment. The reengineering tasks of
   large scale were divided into several subtasks through evolving
   reengineering. XP made these tasks comparatively independent, reduced
