   specifically adapt impedance matching. For multi-band power amplifiers,
   the benefit of operating a SiC or GaN radio frequency (RF) power device
   at high voltage is addressed. All these technologies lead to an analog
   software radio (also called frequency agile radio) where it will turn
   out that such a radio can be realized at less complexity and cost
   compared to a classical digital software radio. Furthermore, it will
   show up that analog software radio technology based on RF-MEMS also has
