   vehicle perception of and maneuver in the land combat environment. This
   effort integrates leading edge military concepts with advanced
   technology development and integration. The program provides a unique
   opportunity to evaluate a group of technically and conceptually
   interdependent initiatives through an iterative series of constructive
   wargames, virtual simulations and field exercises with troops. This
   technology development style shares many features with simulation based
   design and the spiral development model, particularly the exceptionally
   early involvement of the customer (in this instance the military user)
