   At its conclusion in the summer of 2001 Demo III will enable troop
   experimentation with small, highly agile, unmanned vehicles capable of
   off-road, semi-autonomous operation at speeds of up to 32 km/hr during
   daylight and 16 km/hr at night. These capabilities will be integrated
   with navigation, mission planning and target acquisition technologies
